### Offset {#a6d9b5bf6278b280c61b1c37375cad241}

A constant offset to be added to the <a href="/docs/api/classes/anonymous-namespace-loopstrengthreduce-cpp-/lsruse">LSRUse</a> expression.

This allows multiple fixups to share the same <a href="/docs/api/classes/anonymous-namespace-loopstrengthreduce-cpp-/lsruse">LSRUse</a> with different offsets, for example in an unrolled loop.
